-- Table structure for table `InitialCompany`

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `InitialCompany`;
/*!40101 SET @saved_cs_client     = @@character_set_client */;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = utf8 */;
CREATE TABLE `InitialCompany` (
  `InitialCompanyId` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `Email` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FirstName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `LastName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `CompanyName` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Contact` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Message` varchar(5000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `RegistrationInfo` text,
  `Status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `IsComing` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `IsMakeUpTraining` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `LastRegistered` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `LastModified` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`InitialCompanyId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=11 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = @saved_cs_client */;

/*!40101 SET @saved_cs_client     = @@character_set_client */;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = utf8 */;
CREATE TABLE `SkillRelationship` (
  `SkillRelationshipId` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `SkillId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `RelatedId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `Level` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `LastCreated` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `LastModified` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`SkillRelationshipId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = @saved_cs_client */;

-- Dumping data for table `SkillRelationship`
--

/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `SkillRelationship` DISABLE KEYS */;
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `SkillRelationship` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

--
-- Table structure for table `Translation`
--

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `Translation`;
/*!40101 SET @saved_cs_client     = @@character_set_client */;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = utf8 */;
CREATE TABLE `Translation` (
  `TranslationId` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `CultureCode` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `TranslationCode` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `TranslationName` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`TranslationId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = @saved_cs_client */;

--
-- Dumping data for table `Translation`
--

LOCK TABLES `Translation` WRITE;
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `Translation` DISABLE KEYS */;
/*!40000 ALTER TABLE `Translation` ENABLE KEYS */;
UNLOCK TABLES;

--
-- Table structure for table `User`
--

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `User`;
/*!40101 SET @saved_cs_client     = @@character_set_client */;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = utf8 */;
CREATE TABLE `User` (
  `UserId` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `UserTypeId` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '2',
  `UserKey` varchar(36) NOT NULL,
  `Password` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Email` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `FirstName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `MiddleName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `LastName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `DisplayName` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Headline` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Image` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `RegistrationInfo` text,
  `ReferralId` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `LanguageCode` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'EN',
  `FacebookUserId` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `LinkedinUserId` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `IsSendEmailApplication` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `IsSendEmailMessage` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '1',
  `IsProfileUpdated` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `IsEmailActivated` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `IsAccountVerified` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `IsAccountDeactivated` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `LastActivated` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `LastRegistered` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `LastDeactivated` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `LastModified` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`UserId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=220 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
/*!40101 SET character_set_client = @saved_cs_client */;

/*!40101 SET character_set_client = utf8 */;
CREATE TABLE `UserInfo` (
  `UserInfoId` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `UserId` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `Birthdate` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `Gender` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `Nationality` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `IntroductionLink` varchar(500) DEFAULT NULL,
  `SelfIntroduction` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ReasonForLeavingLastJob` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `LookingFor` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `CurrentSalary` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `NoticePeriod` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `InterviewTimeSlots` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `WillingToTravel` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `LateHours` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `LastCreated` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `LastModified` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`UserInfoId`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=182 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
